Description: The "package name" package aims to quantify movement patterns of satellite tagged animals using methods derrived from statistical physics. 
  This package contains R functions to: calculate displacements, plot probability density functions (pdfs) of displacemets, 
  fit distributions of displacemnts to known distribtuons, calculate the root-mean-square (rms) of displacements, etc etc etc... 
